title: Death Race 2 (2010) [1080p]
description:
Death Race 2 (also known as Death Race: Frankenstein Lives or Death Race 2: Frankenstein Lives) is a 2010 American science fiction action film directed by Roel Reiné, written by Tony Giglio and Paul W. S. Anderson. The film is a prequel to Death Race (2008) and is followed by a sequel Death Race 3: Inferno (2013).

The film explore the origins of the first "Frankenstein" car driver, Carl "Luke" Lucas (Luke Goss). Alongside Goss, the film also stars Fred Koehler, Tanit Phoenix, Robin Shou, Lauren Cohan, Danny Trejo, Sean Bean as the villain and Ving Rhames. A direct-to-video film, it received general negative critical reaction
